# Secret policy

- NEVER read `std::env::var("API_KEY")` or similar in consumer code
- ALWAYS resolve secrets via `vox_clavis::resolve_secret(...)`
- Add new secrets to `crates/vox-clavis/src/spec.rs` with `SecretId` + `SecretSpec`
- After secret changes: run `vox ci secret-env-guard` and `vox ci clavis-parity`
- Reference: docs/src/reference/clavis-ssot.md
